stack: React, Remotion, TypeScript

@EXPORTS
BrainMark.tsx: BrainMark — brain puzzle mark from public/logo/logopraut.svg
BrandLogo.tsx: BrandLogo — mark + "PRAUT" wordmark lockup (full|mark|text)
ExplainerSlide.tsx: ExplainerSlide — top 60% visual + bottom 40% text + webcam slot
LiquidGlassPanel.tsx: LiquidGlassPanel — frosted glassmorphism overlay panel
PiPLayout.tsx: PiPLayout — full screen + 18% webcam bottom-left
PrautShortFrame.tsx: PrautShortFrame — 9:16 (1080×1920) brand frame
PrautSquareFrame.tsx: PrautSquareFrame — 1:1 (1080×1080) brand frame
PrautVideoFrame.tsx: PrautVideoFrame — master 16:9 (1920×1080) brand frame
SafeArea.tsx: SafeArea — scale-to-fit container for reference resolution
SlideRoot.tsx: SlideRoot — navy[900] slide background with padding
SpeakerScreenLayout.tsx: SpeakerScreenLayout — speaker 34% / screen 66% split
SplitLayout.tsx: SplitLayout — 2-column layout with configurable ratio
TopBar.tsx: TopBar — 72px bar with BrainMark left, channel info right
TripleLayout.tsx: TripleLayout — 3-column grid for comparisons
WatermarkPraut.tsx: WatermarkPraut — corner watermark (mark + "PRAUT" text)
WebcamPlaceholder.tsx: WebcamPlaceholder — 240×240 green-screen square (#00FF00), bottom-right, keyed out in post-production

@INTERFACES
PrautVideoFrameProps: { episodeNumber? | episodeTitle? | channelName? | tagline? | includeTopBar? | includeWatermark? | frameless? | borderState? | includeBackground? | includeGlass? | children }

@FUNCTIONS
PrautVideoFrame(props) → React.FC
  purpose: master frame with all layers
  side-effects: none

@DEPENDENCIES
internal: styles/tokens | hooks/useScaleToFit | backgrounds/SpiralGalaxy
external: remotion (AbsoluteFill, Img, staticFile)

@STANDARDS
- PrautVideoFrame is outermost wrapper for ALL 16:9 compositions
- Layer order: SpiralGalaxy → LiquidGlassPanel → children → TopBar → (Watermark if enabled)
- PrautVideoFrame defaults: includeWatermark=false (no watermark in production)
- SafeArea handles resolution independence
- WebcamPlaceholder green-screen (#00FF00), 240×240 square, bottom-right — keyed out in post-production
- TopBar: slide-in enter + exit animation
- BrainMark: renders praut-logo.png from public/logo/
- TopBar auto-generates tagline via pickTagline()
